2011-07-06T06:05:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/avision-inc-june-sales-fall-13-56-table-2380-tt.html
AVISION INC (2380)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 13.56% to NT$213,910,000 from NT$247,479,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            213,910          247,479    
YOY%             -13.56%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,467,154        1,486,462   
YOY%              -1.30% 
=================================================================
 